## Limitations
The findings are based on available literature and may not encompass all cultural perspectives on happiness. Additionally, the data is limited to studies and articles accessible online, which may not represent the most recent research developments. Cultural interpretations of happiness are complex and may not be fully captured in the available sources. Further research is needed to explore these nuances in greater depth.